snippet.title: KINGDOM HEARTS HD 2.8 FINAL CHAPTER PROLOGUE ANNOUNCEMENT TRAILER – TGS 2015
snippet.description:
The complete KINGDOM HEARTS saga to date is now in HD! Introducing KINGDOM HEARTS HD 2.8 FINAL CHAPTER PROLOGUE, which contains the newly remastered KINGDOM HEARTS DREAM DROP DISTANCE, the cinematics from KINGDOM HEARTS UNCHAINED CHI , and a special all new chapter taking place after the events of KINGDOM HEARTS BIRTH BY SLEEP. Coming 2016!
